column4: I-75N is shut down at Exit 110 (Winchester Rd) due to investigation of a serious collision at the southern split reportedly involving a semi and a pedestrian.
All northbound traffic is being diverted to Exit 110 to Winchester Rd until further notice.
NOTE:  Access to I-75N from Winchester Rd and from Man O War Blvd also shut down.
Outbound Newtown Pike at New Circle Rd.
